aura (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Compiler scaffold with lex, parse, emit, ns, hist, cfg modules.
  * CLI: compile, validate, lint, generate, init, add, take, mark,
    rewind, ledger, delta, stream, mix, hold, release, sync, dub.
  * Static musl binary — no libc dependency.

